reviewText: I  love Ms Mahalia Jackson, her voice is absolutely "DIVINE" but the quality of the way it was made is absolutely horrible. I WISH I HAD VIEWED IT AS SOON AS I GOT IT I WOULD HAVE SHIPPED IT RIGHT BACK!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! ON THE RATING HER SINGING IS A (5 star of course) but the way it was made its a (2 star)
At last can  you get the clips, that have been available in the 1990 on vhs-tape here on DVD in 'good' sound and -picture quality!
